data.title: Goldman Sachs
data.meta_description: The Goldman Sachs Group, Inc. is a leading global investment banking, securities, and asset and wealth management firm that provides a wide range of financial services.
data.text:
Serving as lead bookrunner to debut a community of communities on the NYSE with its $860M IPO.

Helping open global markets for a leader in premium electric mobility technology in a $507M IPO.

The culture of Goldman Sachs is defined by an unwavering commitment to client service and an unrelenting pursuit of exceptional performance.

Our strategy is anchored in our world-class, interconnected Global Banking & Markets and Asset & Wealth Management franchises, which are uniquely positioned to drive growth and value for shareholders and clients.
